		<title>From Manali Maps to Riverbank Reality &#8211; How Tirthan Became Our Unexpected Retreat</title>
		<link>https://ausnya.com/from-manali-maps-to-riverbank-reality-how-tirthan-became-our-unexpected-retreat</link>
